                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7093" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0234</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8983 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内修外攘：协同数码借力大数据分析破解成本控制之厄</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">To solve internal and external problems: Xie Tong controls costs through big data analysis</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薛建武，宋东岳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安协同数码股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大数据分析；成本控制；产品推广；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Big Data Analysis; Cost Control; Product Promotion</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例中西安协同数码公司旗下的游戏推广SY部门遭遇了产品推广成本居高不下的问题，案例将SY部门面临的产品推广成本控制问题聚焦为外部合作成本控制和内部推广成本控制两方面，描述了SY部门结合大数据的特点，借助大数据分析的角度解决部门面临的具体难题的过程。案例诠释了大数据分析的一般步骤，以及SY部门如何通过大数据分析中的可视化分析、数据挖掘分析、预测性分析等方法，收集产品推广各个环节的数据信息，解决外部合作成本控制和内部推广成本控制中暴露出的数据问题。有了数据积累，SY部门进而能够建立大数据分析体系下的产品推广成本控制方案和发展规划。通过对本案例的学习讨论，学生可以充分理解大数据分析的步骤与方法，充分理解大数据分析在企业中发挥的作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In this case, the game promotion sy Department of Xi&#39;an collaborative digital company has encountered the problem of high product promotion cost. The case focuses the cost control problems faced by sy Department on external cooperation cost control and internal promotion cost control, and describes the process of SY Department solving the specific problems faced by the Department from the Perspective of big data analysis combined with the characteristics of big data. The case explains the general steps of big data analysis and how sy department collects data information of all links of product promotion through visual analysis, data mining analysis and predictive analysis in big data analysis, so as to solve the data problems exposed in external cooperation cost control and internal promotion cost control. With data accumulation, sy department can then establish product promotion cost control scheme and development plan under the big data analysis system. Through the study and discussion of this case, students can fully understand the steps and methods of big data analysis and the role of big data analysis in enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《大数据技术与运用》、《企业管理信息系统应用》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大数据分析的概念；大数据的特点；大数据分析的步骤；大数据分析的方法；大数据分析的风险数据沼泽</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
